data.title: Ministry
data.meta_description:
Ministry.
Los Angeles, California.
Born in 1981 in Chicago, Ministry has been a lifetime project of Al Jourgensen. Identifiable by its synth-pop sound on Wax Trax! & first LP With Sympathy (1983) A harsher sound appeared on Twitch (1986) The Land of Rape and Honey (1988) The Mind Is A Terrible Thing To Taste (1989) & Psalm 69 (1992) Albums followed with the recent AmeriKKKant (2018) Moral Hygiene (2021) & HOPIUMFORTHEMASSES (2024)
